video.title: Power Rangers Zeo
video.synopsis: This "Mighty Morphin Power Rangers" spinoff finds Tommy and the gang battling new enemies, using abilities acquired from the Zeo Crystal.

episodes.synopsis: In the rubble of the destroyed Command Center, the Power Rangers find the Zeo Crystal.
episodes.title: A Zeo Beginning: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: With King Mondo preparing to invade the solar system, the Rangers face their greatest challenge.
episodes.title: A Zeo Beginning: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: When Mondo and Machina unleash the Staroid on the Zeo Rangers, they are forced to call on their untested Zeo Zords.
episodes.title: The Shooting Star

episodes.synopsis: The Cogs steal the computer software that Rocky and his friend Jennifer are working on and use it against the Rangers.
episodes.title: Target Rangers

episodes.synopsis: Tommy and Katherine take care of a baby for a school assignment, giving King Mondo an idea for his evil ambitions.
episodes.title: For Cryin' Out Loud

episodes.synopsis: The baseball team is the perfect outlet for Prince Sprocket to battle the Power Rangers when he turns the batting machine into the People Pitcher.
episodes.title: Rangers in the Outfield

episodes.synopsis: A specially trained dog named Smokey aids the Zeo Rangers in fighting Digster, Mondo and Machina's latest monster.
episodes.title: Every Dog Has His Day

episodes.synopsis: When Ernie brings a puppet show to the Youth Center to entertain the kids, Mondo and Machina hatch a plan to control the children's minds.
episodes.title: The Puppet Blaster

episodes.synopsis: Prince Sprocket recruits the Rangers to appear in his twisted movie, "Invasion of the Ranger Snatchers.
episodes.title: Invasion of the Ranger Snatchers

episodes.synopsis: As Billy is about to graduate from Angel Grove High, Cestro, the Blue Alien Ranger, lands on Earth seeking Billy's help.
episodes.title: Graduation Blues

episodes.synopsis: As Rocky and Adam work on developing hybrid plants for class, Rocky's plant begins growing rapidly and seems to have an appetite for metal.
episodes.title: A Few Bad Seeds

episodes.synopsis: Prince Sprocket and King Mondo pursue a mysterious musician at Angel Grove High.
episodes.title: Instrument of Destruction

episodes.synopsis: When Tanya and Adam run into a computer virus, Mondo hatches a plan to create Mean Screen, a horrible computer monster.
episodes.title: Mean Screen

episodes.synopsis: As Billy is returning from Aquitar, Machina and Mondo attack his spacecraft, sending it into the gravitational pull of the Machine Skybase.
episodes.title: Mr. Billy's Wild Ride

episodes.synopsis: Tommy receives a "Dear John" letter.
episodes.title: There's No Business Like Snow Business: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Mondo and Machina send the Defoliator to create a greenhouse effect in Angel Grove.
episodes.title: There's No Business Like Snow Business: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: As Katherine tries to console Tommy about his letter from Kimberly, a spark of attraction begins to form between the two Rangers.
episodes.title: There's No Business Like Snow Business: Part 3

episodes.synopsis: While on a journey to find True of Heart, Tommy meets a young man who looks just like the old mystic.
episodes.title: Inner Spirit

episodes.synopsis: While searching for the other half of an arrowhead, Tommy discovers that its owner is his brother.
episodes.title: Challenges

episodes.synopsis: King Mondo tries to blackmail Tommy into giving up his arrowhead by holding his newfound brother captive.
episodes.title: Found and Lost

episodes.synopsis: With both halves of the arrowhead in his possession, King Mondo vows to destroy the Zeo Rangers while continuing to hold Tommy's brother hostage.
episodes.title: Brother, Can You Spare an Arrowhead?

episodes.synopsis: King Mondo sends the Defector robot to trick the Zeo Rangers and gain their trust so that he can destroy them.
episodes.title: Trust in Me

episodes.synopsis: While watching a monster movie, Adam falls asleep and envisions his fellow Rangers as hideous monsters.
episodes.title: It Came from Angel Grove

episodes.synopsis: Prince Sprocket comes to Earth to fight the Zeo Rangers with his new toy, the Googleheimer robot.
episodes.title: Bulk Fiction

episodes.synopsis: The Zeo Rangers fight to save Angel Grove from Prince Sprocket and his new birthday toy, the Wrecking Ball.
episodes.title: Song Sung Yellow

episodes.synopsis: King Mondo attempts to rule the Earth's waterways by building a fleet of ships under an invisible field.
episodes.title: Game of Honor

episodes.synopsis: The appearance of the Gold Ranger spoils King Mondo's plan to divide and conquer the Zeo Rangers.
episodes.title: The Power of Gold

episodes.synopsis: Prince Sprocket shrinks the Rangers and puts them in a terrarium with a hungry tarantula -- until the Gold Ranger comes to the rescue.
episodes.title: A Small Problem

episodes.synopsis: When the Rangers and their friend Raymond help Ernie set up for a banquet, they learn how different cultures celebrate the holidays.
episodes.title: A Season to Remember

episodes.synopsis: The evil Leaky Faucet monster pollutes Angel Grove's waters with toxic oil and seeks to destroy Katherine during a surfing contest.
episodes.title: Oily to Bed, Oily to Rise

episodes.synopsis: The Somnibot casts a sleeping spell on the people of Angel Grove, leaving it up to the Gold Ranger to stop the evil sandman.
episodes.title: Rock-a-Bye Power Rangers

episodes.synopsis: The Gold Ranger finds asylum in the Power Chamber from the evil Mondo, Machina and the Varox bounty hunter.
episodes.title: Do I Know You?

episodes.synopsis: When Varox bounty hunters attack the Gold Ranger, Pyramidas is hit and falls into the seas of the planet Aquitar.
episodes.title: Revelations of Gold

episodes.synopsis: Time is running out for transference of the golden powers.
episodes.title: A Golden Homecoming

episodes.synopsis: King Mondo is determined to use the Damocles Sword to destroy the Zeo Rangers.
episodes.title: Mondo's Last Stand

episodes.synopsis: As the teens are helping Ernie set up for his new Beach Club, a group of young toughs rides in and begins to trash the place.
episodes.title: Bomber in the Summer

episodes.synopsis: The teens take part in a charity fashion show for Mr. Stenchy, a famous designer.
episodes.title: Scent of a Weasel

episodes.synopsis: Aisha sends Tanya a map of Mysterio Island, where her parents may have vanished years earlier.
episodes.title: The Lore of Auric

episodes.synopsis: When Katherine stages a ballet about King Midas, Louie Kaboom creates the Midas Hound, an idol that changes everything into gold.
episodes.title: The Ranger Who Came in from the Gold

episodes.synopsis: Louie Kaboom vows to take the helm of the Machine Empire.
episodes.title: The Joke's on Blue

episodes.synopsis: In an effort to break up the Zeo Rangers, Prince Gasket abducts Tommy while he's jet skiing on the lake.
episodes.title: Where in the World Is Zeo Ranger Five?

episodes.synopsis: The Zeo Rangers discover that Tommy has been captured by Prince Gasket and placed in a large arena with monsters battling one another.
episodes.title: King for a Day: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Gold Ranger is forced to defend himself when the brainwashed Tommy attacks him.
episodes.title: King for a Day: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Tommy is confused when he repeatedly relives his experiences of the day.
episodes.title: A Brief Mystery of Time

episodes.synopsis: The teens all dress in classic mystery-character costumes when they participate in a charity event organized by Det. Stone.
episodes.title: A Mystery to Me

episodes.synopsis: Tommy asks Tanya for voice lessons when he has to sing in front of the class.
episodes.title: Another Song and Dance

episodes.synopsis: Everyone is stunned when it's revealed that Billy has aged rapidly and turned into an old man.
episodes.title: Rangers of Two Worlds: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Zeo Rangers team with the Alien Rangers of Aquitar to combat a double threat from King Mondo and Lord Zedd.
episodes.title: Rangers of Two Worlds: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The golden powers start to fade from Jason.
episodes.title: Hawaii Zeo

episodes.synopsis: As Jason continues to lose the golden powers, he's confronted by Rita and Lord Zedd.
episodes.title: Good as Gold
